<div role=3D"note" class=3D"hatnote navigation-not-searchable">This article=
 is about the genre in general. For other uses, see <a href=3D"https://en.w=
ikipedia.org/wiki/Zombie_apocalypse_(disambiguation)" class=3D"mw-disambig"=
